[30;1m616 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m617 | [0m[35mdef knot_removal(degree, knotvector, ctrlpts, u, **kwargs):[0m
[30;1m618 | [0m[35m    """ Computes the control points of the rational/non-rational spline after knot removal.[0m
[30;1m619 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m620 | [0m[35m    Implementation based on Algorithm A5.8 and Equation 5.28 of The NURBS Book by Piegl & Tiller[0m
[30;1m621 | [0m[35m[0m

[31m--[ [0m[34mMatch #[0m[33m280[0m[34m of [0m[33m1111[0m[31m ]--[0m
   Rule Id: [34mBD000600[0m
       Tag: [34mSecurity.Backdoor.LOLBAS.Windows[0m

[30;1m496 | [0m[35mdef knot_insertion(degree, knotvector, ctrlpts, u, **kwargs):[0m
[30;1m497 | [0m[35m    """ Computes the control points of the rational/non-rational spline after knot insertion.[0m

[30;1m260 | [0m[35m    recursion formula.[0m
[30;1m261 | [0m[35m[0m

[30;1m115 | [0m[35mdef make_quadtree(points, size_u, size_v, **kwargs):[0m
[30;1m116 | [0m[35m    """ Generates a quadtree-like structure from surface control points.[0m
